1. Abstract
-----------
Modify the C model compiler to be compliant  with the MISRA-C (2004) standard.
Run a compliance checker (e.g. QA-C) on generated C code from test models.  Modify the model compiler templates to increase compliance.  Document areas of uncompliance.

